com.twitter.sdk.android.core.internal.scribe

Class EventsFilesManager<T>

  • Object
    • com.twitter.sdk.android.core.internal.scribe.EventsFilesManager<T>

  • public abstract class EventsFilesManager<T>
extends Object
    Manages files containing events. This includes, writing events to them and periodically (size or time triggered) rolling them over to a target directory.
